{
  "message": "test(conformance): expand ufunc metamorphic cases 25\u219236\n\nAdd metamorphic relations beyond commutativity and linearity:\n- Associativity: (a + b) + c == a + (b + c), (a * b) * c == a * (b * c)\n- Distributivity: a * (b + c) == a*b + a*c\n- Double negation: --a == a\n- Identity elements: a + 0 == a, a * 1 == a\n- Inverse operations: a - a == 0, a / a == 1\n- Reduction invariants: sum(a) == sum(a.T), prod(a) == prod(a.T)\n- Decomposition: sum(concat(a, b)) == sum(a) + sum(b)\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
